Requires-Dist: numpy

A simulator for QCIS.

```python
from qcis_sim import run


qcis_str = """
H Q22
H Q27
X Q27
Y Q27
Z Q27
S Q27
SD Q27
T Q27
TD Q27
CZ Q27 Q22
B Q1 Q4
I Q1 0.1
RX Q22 0.2
RY Q22 0.2
RZ Q10 0.2

M Q22
M Q27
"""


print(run(qcis_str, shots=100, topo=True))
# topo: topological check
```
